NBA ALL-STAR WEEKEND
February 18, 2011
DeMar DeRozan
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







 Q. How does it feel to be here?
 DeMAR DeROZAN: It feels good. Just coming out here, back in my hometown representing for my team. Just go out there and try to do the best I can. 

 Q. How close are the Raptors to being back in the mix?
 DeMAR DeROZAN: Oh, we are definitely close. We have been better every day. We can't do nothing but get better.
 Just trying to get better and working better to be the best player I can be and come out with something new. I want to be great at every aspect of my game. Come out to be the best player that I can be. 





END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT